{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story</h2><br>Meet Ethan, a man who awakens in a mysterious place with no memory of how he got there, except for his name. His companion is Sarah, a woman who is also in the same predicament. As they explore their surroundings, they realize that they are trapped in a terrifying purgatory.<br><br>Ethan is determined to uncover the truth behind their imprisonment and find a way to escape. However, as he delve deeper into the secrets of the purgatory, Ethan soon realize that there are dark and sinister forces at play. Will they be able to escape with their lives, or will they become trapped in the purgatory forever?<br><br>Innocents Purgatory is a bone-chilling first-person RPG, where you must use your wits and skills to uncover the mysteries of this hellish world. Explore every nook and cranny of the purgatory, uncover hidden secrets, and encounter terrifying creatures along the way. Will you be able to find a way out, or will you succumb to the horrors of the Purgatory?<br><br><strong>Melee combat the evil spirits of the purgatory.</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2169270/extras/CombatGif.gif?t=1695229775\" /><br><br><strong>Use magic to gain an advantage over your opponents.</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2169270/extras/NewMagicGif.gif?t=1695229775\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome to the Purgatory","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2169270/a7d16e367850d9aa8937c36e43700511df3d83b2.jpg"},{"name":"Soul seeker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2169270/d65f481484bcefc211be984dee8fa3a45674ddd5.jpg"},{"name":"Soul detective","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2169270/b4c865a865b236e522bb7cf4ddd2b6ed16f4f503.jpg"},{"name":"It's a miracle?",